cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software, please cite it as below."
type: software
title: "kamino-vault-counterfactuals"
abstract: >-
  Historical replay + counterfactual stress testing for Kamino Lend reserves
  and obligations on Solana. Six pure-function detectors (oracle-staleness,
  collateral-cascade, depositor-exit-shock, utilization-band-breach,
  liquidation-latency, LTV-distribution-stress). Mirror of
  morpho-vault-counterfactuals adapted for the Solana account model.
authors:
